    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p></p>\n<p>\nGiven 2 arrays <b>A</b>, <b>B</b> (1-indexed) each having length <b>N</b>. There are 2 types of queries. You have to handle <b>Q</b> of them.<br>\n<ul>\n<li>Type 1 : 1 L<br>\nAdd the subarray <b>B<sub>1</sub>, B<sub>2</sub>, B<sub>3</sub> ... B<sub>N-L+1</sub></b> to <b>A<sub>L</sub>, A<sub>L+1</sub>, A<sub>L+2</sub> ... A<sub>N</sub></b> respectively.<br>\ni.e. Add <b>B<sub>1</sub></b> to <b>A<sub>L</sub></b>, <b>B<sub>2</sub></b> to <b>A<sub>L+1</sub></b> ... <b>B<sub>N-L+1</sub></b> to <b>A<sub>N</sub></b>.<br>\n</li><br>\n\n<li>Type 2 : 2 L R<br>\nPrint the sum <b>A<sub>L</sub> + A<sub>L+1</sub> + A<sub>L+2</sub> + ... A<sub>R</sub></b><br>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n\n<p></p>\n\n<h3>Input Format:</h3> \nFirst line of the input contains two space separated integer denoting <b>N</b>, <b>Q</b> respectively.<br>\nNext 2 lines of the input, each containing <b>N</b> space separating integers, denotes array <b>A</b> and array <b>B</b> respectively.\nNext <b>Q</b> lines describes a query. Each query starts with a integer <b>t</b>, denoting the type of query and contains one or two integer depending on type of query as described in the problem statement.\n\n<h3>Output Format:</h3>\nFor each query of type 2 print the answer.\n\n<h3>Constraints:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>1<= <b>N</b> <=200000</li>\n<li>1<= <b>Q</b> <=200000</li>\n<li>1<= <b>A<sub>i</sub></b> <=100000</li>\n<li>1<= <b>B<sub>i</sub></b> <=100000</li>\n<li>1<= <b>t</b> <=2</li>\n<li>For type 1 query, <b>1 <= L <= N</b> </li>\n<li>For type 2 query, <b>1 <= L <= R <= N</b> </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Sample Input:</h3>\n4 3<br>\n1 2 1 4<br>\n2 1 2 3<br>\n1 2<br>\n2 1 1<br>\n2 2 4\n\n<h3>Sample Output:</h3>\n1<br>\n12",
